This is how to is_equal_to_sum_even of n:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 2
   Do this n times:
      When i is less than n, then:
         When remainder of i and 2 is 0, then:
            Remember that total is sum of total and i
         End when
         Increase i
      End when
   End do
   When total is n, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when
   The answer is 0
